dct_title_s: Active Planning Zones: San Mateo County, California, 2014
dct_description_sm: This polygon shapefile depicts land areas, or zones, for which planning is actively taking place as of November 18, 2014. Zones can also dictate permitted uses and restrictions for any new development in these areas, such as height, density and purpose of structures. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for San Mateo County, California.
This coverage can be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analyses of geospatial data.
The County of San Mateo cannot vouch for the data or analyses derived from these data.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
